## Technologies Used

### Frontend

- **React.js** ‚Äì Building dynamic user interfaces.
- **TailwindCSS** ‚Äì Utility‚Äëfirst CSS for rapid styling.
- **Vite** ‚Äì Fast development and build optimizations.
- **Framer Motion** ‚Äì Smooth, interactive animations.
- **Lucide Icons** ‚Äì Elegant, lightweight icons.

### Backend

- **Node.js** ‚Äì JavaScript runtime.
- **Express.js** ‚Äì API framework.
- **Google Sheets API** ‚Äì Data storage integration.
- **CORS & Body-Parser** ‚Äì Managing requests and cross‚Äëorigin access.

